comments: One of my easiest classes. she is the nicest women ever. i am taking her again for another class

Really enjoyed this class. Test were super easy if you made flash cards and or studied. Gives bonus in class for answering questions. She is hard to understand but if you ask her to repeat she doesnt mind to help out!

Her tests really aren\'t hard at all though.. she tells you exactly what will be on them. However,she will rush you while you are taking them. Her class is extremely boring and attendance is mandatory. She\'s very hard to understand and mutters to herself a lot. I passed her class w/ an A, but it was a very miserable semester bc of her class.

absolute horrible teacher! there is a test every day, and she always complained about how horrible the class was as students and that we took too long to take the test. she also kept us after class atleast 5 minutes every day
